<article class="main banner">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="sixcol">
      </div>
      <div class="sixcol last">
        <div class="quote-container">
          <h1 class="red">Are you a Spoke Geek?</h1>
          
          <p class="founder-quote gray">&ldquo;Riding is a great for getting the heart rate up, exploring new places, chatting with friends... It&rsquo;s like golf. Except it&rsquo;s a workout and I know how to ride a bike.&rdquo; - Wil Everts, Club Founder</p>
          <p class="gray">Spoke Geek is a casual cycling club for SF start-up geeks and friends. All are welcome to join our group rides and Strava. Sign up below to receive the Strava Club password and monthly ride alerts via email (<em>we promise not to spam you or sell your information</em>.)</p>

          <div class="mailchimp">
